# 003 - Deploy Agent on Linux

* [Deploy agent](https://docs.sensu.io/sensu-go/latest/operations/deploy-sensu/install-sensu/#install-sensuctl)

```
# Setup Sensu Ctl

```
curl -s https://packagecloud.io/install/repositories/sensu/stable/script.deb.sh | sudo bash
```

# Install the sensu-go-cli package

```  
sudo apt-get install sensu-go-cli
```

```sensuctl configure -n \
--username 'admin' \
--password '1qa2ws3eD!' \
--namespace default \
--url 'http://10.0.99.10:8080'
```
